Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.50,0:00:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为追回GUNDAM2号机
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.20,0:00:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔比昂向星海中进发
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.50,0:00:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星之沧海
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.00,0:00:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就如同在考验这些年轻人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.10,0:00:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在那里等待他们的是新的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.10,0:00:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年战争的怨念
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.95,0:00:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化做惊涛骇浪向浦木袭来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.80,0:00:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逐渐损毁的GUNDAM1号机
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.40,0:00:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪拉兹响彻四方的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.70,0:00:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面对处于困境的浦木
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.20,0:00:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.25,0:00:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜的心中确实捕捉到了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.00,0:02:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)\fs60}冯·布朗的战士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.90,0:02:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再派一个人来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.10,0:02:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.80,0:02:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要到冯·布朗了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.30,0:02:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直是体无完肤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.95,0:03:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿纳海姆的人可要高兴得流眼泪了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.25,0:03:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过阿尔比昂没被击沉已是万幸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.34,0:03:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托那家伙的福吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阴沉的小子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.65,0:03:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过总算能得到上陆许可了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.26,0:03:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.94,0:03:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.20,0:03:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.40,0:03:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我约会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.90,0:03:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么说增援是没指望了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.00,0:03:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在联邦军的体质因保守而变得僵硬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.70,0:03:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幕僚们对迪拉兹舰队的评价也太乐观
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.90,0:03:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我的权限无法再多调派舰只了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.30,0:03:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请谅解
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.87,0:03:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席那普斯大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.29,0:03:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在只能靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.66,0:03:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请尽力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.05,0:03:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.50,0:03:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等迪拉兹发难之后就太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.06,0:03:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冯·布朗港湾管理局来电
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.92,0:04:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给予第一区宇宙港的入港许可
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.68,0:04:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭乘往香港于16:20起飞的班机佛罗伊德的乘客
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.20,0:04:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空气真新鲜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.46,0:04:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再有妮娜小姐陪着的话就完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.35,0:04:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又被甩了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.10,0:04:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混、混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.63,0:04:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜小姐在工作啊，工作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.10,0:04:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.30,0:04:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨！妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.91,0:04:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.70,0:05:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.62,0:05:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.60,0:05:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美女如云
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.18,0:05:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是妮娜的同伴？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.07,0:05:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来，妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.40,0:05:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.20,0:05:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说了，很辛苦吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.30,0:05:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常务
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.40,0:05:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴普尔顿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.90,0:05:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平安归来比什么都好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.56,0:05:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是劳您操心了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.55,0:05:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.60,0:05:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟出动重力下用的机型去参加空间战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.90,0:05:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是我的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.47,0:05:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长下达的1号机的宇宙用换装
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.62,0:05:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,及整修要赶在后天前完成
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.20,0:05:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后天？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.77,0:05:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,困难的要求啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.70,0:05:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吗？妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.15,0:05:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常务，我也要拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.55,0:05:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我来做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.96,0:05:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将至今为止的数据连同报告书送到我这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.27,0:05:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明早要看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.50,0:05:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.79,0:06:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到夜晚了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.54,0:06:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5907…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.90,0:06:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以米诺夫斯基粒子散布的浓度就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.15,0:06:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，司考特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.30,0:06:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也想想别的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.95,0:06:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什、什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.40,0:06:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.97,0:06:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醉了，西蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.60,0:06:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴宁格大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.48,0:06:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不、不好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.40,0:06:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去其他地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.90,0:06:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴宁格大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.65,0:06:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.00,0:06:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有喝？宏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.50,0:07:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽情地喝啊，尽情地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.10,0:07:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好很好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.70,0:07:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时登场的就是联邦的王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.60,0:07:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙夏大爷我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.30,0:07:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.40,0:07:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.80,0:07:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把迪拉兹舰队的家伙们抓了扔、抓了扔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.50,0:07:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那GUNDAM是你驾驶的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.51,0:07:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.08,0:07:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM被弄坏了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.80,0:07:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为被菜鸟机师驾驶了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.80,0:07:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.45,0:07:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真会给阿纳海姆添麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.70,0:07:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻夜修理呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还好意思悠闲地喝酒？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.80,0:07:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是怕看到坏掉的GUNDAM会难受？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.64,0:07:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙、蒙夏中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.45,0:07:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样啊？少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.05,0:07:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.10,0:07:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真狼狈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.20,0:08:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺盛气凌人的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.80,0:08:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦军的老兄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撞了人也不打声招呼吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.80,0:09:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会把这儿当成地球了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.50,0:09:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是月球
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.84,0:09:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是谁都要向联邦摇尾乞怜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.40,0:09:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，该我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.71,0:09:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说晚安还早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.20,0:09:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.84,0:09:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.30,0:09:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.80,0:09:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是MS机师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.35,0:09:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还、还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.07,0:09:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多锻炼锻炼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.28,0:09:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然会死在迪拉兹舰队手上的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.25,0:10:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.62,0:10:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.05,0:10:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有点难度呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.40,0:10:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来杯咖啡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.00,0:10:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.90,0:10:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.60,0:10:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你勤奋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.40,0:10:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不偶尔透透气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.05,0:10:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可会燃烧殆尽的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.30,0:10:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.66,0:11:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在为以前的事赌气吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.40,0:11:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎、怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.70,0:11:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再谈个恋爱就行了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.06,0:11:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能使恋爱、工作两不误的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.20,0:11:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.70,0:11:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是想嫁给GUNDAM吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.34,0:11:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.80,0:12:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请、请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.10,0:12:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有食欲吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.90,0:12:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗把脸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.16,0:12:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.90,0:12:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭候大驾，来得真快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.78,0:12:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿纳海姆也挺会做生意的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.70,0:12:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大主顾联邦的船在第一港口
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.68,0:13:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边却是资源搬入港？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.80,0:13:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎哟，这事没传达给您吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.40,0:13:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后得给我联络得彻底点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.73,0:13:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的补给舰入港时
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是再有联邦军严阵以待的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.20,0:13:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把殖民地扔到月球上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.80,0:13:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会铭记在心的，希玛大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.01,0:13:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.27,0:13:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.50,0:13:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军人的话就别说“在下”！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.43,0:13:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.56,0:13:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是逃兵吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.00,0:13:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天似乎有联邦军的舰只入港
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.05,0:14:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉托拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不喝咖啡了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.13,0:14:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚饭还要麻烦你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.06,0:14:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚饭准备我的就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.15,0:14:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.67,0:14:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫宏·浦木
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.43,0:14:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS的机师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.45,0:14:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么逃出来？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.10,0:14:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕战斗了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.15,0:14:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.26,0:14:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但都怪我才使MS…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.75,0:14:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别干了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.94,0:14:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样想的话就趁早的好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.50,0:14:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那、那要是能行的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.66,0:14:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这、这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.70,0:14:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年战争时的MA？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs34\3c&H00ef877e}MA：Mobile All-Range Maneuverability Offence\N Utility Reinforcement(全领域泛用支援机动兵器)的缩写
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.70,0:14:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这东西还能动的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.15,0:14:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.80,0:15:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.78,0:15:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这东西是废品
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.00,0:15:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的嗜好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.05,0:15:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准再靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.50,0:15:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木仍旧没有联络吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.92,0:15:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.55,0:15:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.80,0:15:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个会添乱的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.30,0:15:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分这么多层啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了下层的话可就棘手了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.00,0:15:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过最下层只有工厂和废品店啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.00,0:15:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听不懂我的话吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.86,0:15:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子再不适可而止的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.61,0:15:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这块基板过热烧毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.80,0:15:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得更换才行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.10,0:15:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.35,0:15:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没钱雇人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.83,0:15:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.12,0:16:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就请让我在此多待几天作为补偿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.54,0:16:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不回船上去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.46,0:16:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.01,0:16:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为在被说成逃兵之前，一直没发觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.15,0:16:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.57,0:16:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了，直说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.80,0:16:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有这些部件就能搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.74,0:16:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.03,0:16:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会搞来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.10,0:16:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.14,0:16:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没找到宏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.40,0:16:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边也毫无音信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.50,0:16:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.77,0:17:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉托拉女士…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.93,0:17:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你何时…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.36,0:17:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.86,0:17:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你要帮敌人？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.80,0:17:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.70,0:17:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为没法修好凯利都快放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.96,0:17:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是联邦军吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.96,0:17:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想让他收留我一阵子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.07,0:17:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你是逃兵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.00,0:17:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是凯利
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.67,0:17:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一年战争中失去了一只手臂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.80,0:17:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此被撤离了MS
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.70,0:17:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的斗志还没燃尽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.70,0:17:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯利先生曾是机师…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.80,0:18:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂，请接入港联邦军的船
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.23,0:18:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天入港的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.60,0:18:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于太空住民衷心企求自治权的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.50,0:18:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦行使其强大的军事力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.60,0:18:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将那萌芽扼杀在摇篮之中的企图
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.80,0:18:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有足够的事实来加以证明
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.00,0:18:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.78,0:18:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我们的战果
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.81,0:19:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这架GUNDAM是以核攻击为目的而开发的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.50,0:19:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这架违反南极条约的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.03,0:19:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其存在本身便足以证明联邦的险恶意图
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.90,0:19:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.77,0:19:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.66,0:19:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是那么软弱的男人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.00,0:19:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比想象中更上等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.25,0:19:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里竟然有如此东西沉睡着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.50,0:20:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过以你的身体…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.53,0:20:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在改造成单手也能操纵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.47,0:20:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.29,0:20:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是凯利·雷兹那大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.80,0:20:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这东西能参与星尘作战的话就太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.20,0:20:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪、迪拉兹舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.55,0:20:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过来得及吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.00,0:20:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的船明天出港
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.36,0:20:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶不上的话就无法参加作战了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.36,0:20:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明、明天？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.70,0:20:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.73,0:20:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.05,0:20:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.20,0:20:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯利先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.95,0:20:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.76,0:20:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸色都变了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.20,0:20:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那些家伙是迪拉兹舰队的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.56,0:20:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你曾是ZION的机师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.28,0:20:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷听可不礼貌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.02,0:20:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.68,0:21:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我可没求你留下或修理MA啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.40,0:21:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉托拉女士也在担心你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.67,0:21:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这种窝囊废没资格批评我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.61,0:21:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不甘心吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.95,0:21:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不甘心就放马过来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.90,0:21:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则就夹起尾巴快滚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.64,0:21:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.30,0:21:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯利
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.00,0:21:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.90,0:21:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.22,0:21:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.44,0:21:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.81,0:21:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能那样，凯利先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.41,0:21:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会成为丧家之犬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.64,0:21:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管发生什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.58,0:21:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.70,0:21:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之你走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.74,0:22:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是摩拉联络我的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.74,0:22:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说你似乎在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.60,0:22:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是忙于阿纳海姆的工作吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.50,0:22:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若不偶尔透透气，会否燃烧殆尽呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.35,0:22:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心情好点了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.35,0:22:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回阿尔比昂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.26,0:22:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.70,0:22:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不能回去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.20,0:22:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有事没做完
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.70,0:22:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深深沉在心底挥之不去的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.20,0:22:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.20,0:22:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.63,0:22:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我保证
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.10,0:22:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你也转告舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.10,0:22:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.50,0:22:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你特地来找我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.10,0:22:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.27,0:22:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM的测试在阿纳海姆的利巴莫工厂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.81,0:23:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上午10点
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.70,0:23:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么回来？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.60,0:23:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会回船上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.54,0:23:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前我想修好它
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.87,0:23:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怜悯吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.34,0:23:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.80,0:23:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想过了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.57,0:23:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若就此不干机师
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.83,0:23:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己会怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.20,0:23:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摆弄机械来维持生计…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.66,0:23:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.20,0:23:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉托拉就希望我那么过一生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.20,0:23:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样当个废品店老板也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.40,0:23:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这么想过
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.40,0:23:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.36,0:23:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.27,0:23:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这样干废品店的工作，也会有某种…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.06,0:23:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得这里并不是自己归宿的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.70,0:23:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我心底深处会有…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.41,0:24:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我终究是个机师的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.92,0:24:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是这样想
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.05,0:24:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再见时我们就是敌人了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.25,0:24:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那一拳很有力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.50,0:24:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏·浦木少尉现在返回执行任务
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.32,0:24:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.46,0:24:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.10,0:25:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM1号机-Full Burnern
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.49,0:25:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出动
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.70,0:28:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预    告
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.79,0:28:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM1号机做为Full Burnern复活了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.04,0:28:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木再次站在它的身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.80,0:28:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此而振奋不已的妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.49,0:28:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.49,0:28:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运没有停止对人们的磨练
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.01,0:28:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对妮娜、凯利、浦木
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.33,0:28:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缠绕着的绳索没有丝毫松动
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.23,0:28:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.95,0:28:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月面上的攻防战即将拉开序幕
